{"tid":155788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★廢老末日！香港或於三年後終止 2G 網絡服務！","createTime":"2017-03-14T10:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T13:27:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37cafa7cf71b8343eaa5227b5bfe8ee70c4b4c86","tid":155788,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"留意目前 2G 網絡只支援 900 兆赫（MHz）及 1,800 兆赫雙頻譜，而當中有 198.6 兆赫頻譜的現有指配期將會於 2020 年 11 月至 2021 年 9 月期間屆滿，再加上 1.4 兆赫閒置頻譜，因此政府目前正就相關頻譜重新指配進行公眾諮詢。而在立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會會議上，雖然通訊局表示不排除有旅客會繼續採用 2G 網絡，但若然三年後 2G 用戶人數大減，他們或會考慮要求營運商決定是否中止 2G 服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/14/re-assignment-of-2g-spectrum/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F14%2Fre-assignment-of-2g-spectrum%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=8a3f41ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/14/re-assignment-of-2g-spectrum/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"b5e77962686b94e96fd1057f744ec5c5c15a5062","tid":155788,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4974d2c2e076bda39c08dc36b57d6e70b5501735","tid":155788,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"星加坡今年就停2G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b221ef22bba5e178ed619f9d0c76dfc0c26823ac","tid":155788,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"馬交前兩年都停左"},{"pid":"1ed94433de7120a7094a855d5f0a14d67baa5aaa","tid":155788,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"雙卡雙待手提電話，第2張卡多數行2G （4G/3G + 2G） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870f4ca6aff0ba3c608ebadb4a481e2c2a2be7da","tid":155788,"uid":79495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"廢老